  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT20">
<l>nīyē yulakelā niṉṉaruḷē niṟpaṉavu</l>
<l>nīyē tavattēva tēvaṉu nīyē</l>
<l>yericuṭaru mālvaraiyu meṇṭicaiyum aṇṭat</l>
<l>tirucuṭaru māya vivai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are all the worlds; [all] that remains is [due to] Your grace;</l>
<l>You are the God of gods [with] penance; You are all these:</l>
<l>the burning fire, the big mountains, the eight directions,</l>
<l>the two lights of the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
